about.summary: Exclude specific directories from nosetests runs.

name: nose-exclude
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "nose-exclude" %}
{% set version = "0.5.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f78fa8b41eeb815f0486414f710f1eea0949e346cfb11d59ba6295ed69e84304

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - nose
    - python
    - setuptools

test:
  imports:
    - nose_exclude

about:
  home: https://github.com/kgrandis/nose-exclude
  license: LGPL-2.1
  license_family: LGPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Exclude specific directories from nosetests runs.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - xhochy
